HEADWORD: Cosmetical
<hw>Cos*met"ic*al</hw>
<pr>(-?-k<it>a</it>l)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>kosmitiko`s</grk> skilled in decorating, fr. <grk>ko`smos</grk>
order, ornament: cf. F. <ets>cosm⟦eacute⟧tique</ets>. See
<er>Cosmos</er>.]</ety> <def>Imparting or improving beauty, particularly
